Project: TimerApps-CLI
Version: 0.0.1
Author: RaihanZxx (Raihan Zaky)
Email: raihanzxzy@gmail.com
Repository: https://github.com/RaihanZxx/TimerApps-CLI
Created: October 2024

Description:
TimerApps-CLI is a command-line application for Termux that helps users limit
app usage on Android devices to reduce distractions and increase productivity.
The application supports both rooted and non-rooted devices with ADB support.

Features:
- Smart timer pause/resume functionality
- Automatic app killing or freezing when limits are reached
- Daily timer auto-reset
- Termux API notifications
- Interactive dashboard and CLI interfaces
- Persistent usage database and logging
- Battery-efficient monitoring

Contributors:
- RaihanZxx - Original Author & Developer

For more information, visit: https://github.com/RaihanZxx/TimerApps-CLI
